<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Pet Care Center</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f5fbff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #17a2b8;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .section-title {
      color: #17a2b8;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #17a2b8;
    }

    .card-title {
      color: #17a2b8;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #343a40;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Pet Care Center</h1>
    <p>Learn about different pets and how to take care of them.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="section-title">Our Friendly Pets</h2>

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">🐶 Dog</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
              Dogs are loyal friends. They enjoy playing, walking, and spending time with people.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">🐱 Cat</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
              Cats are playful and independent. They love sleeping and exploring their surroundings.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">🐰 Rabbit</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
              Rabbits enjoy eating fresh vegetables and hopping around in open spaces.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid footer">
    <p>Made with Bootstrap — Card Practice</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
